Pre-Game Insights: Cyprus is coming off a terrible Euro 2024 qualifying campaign where they lost all eight matches.
The island nation's wait for a first major international appearance continues, with the 2024-25 UEFA Nations League scheduled for June.
Latvia lost all but one game in their Euro qualifying campaign last year, finishing at the bottom of Group D with just three points from eight games.
Miscellaneous Highlights: This is the first meeting between Cyprus and Latvia since 1997.
Cyprus will be looking to improve their recent poor form and prepare for the upcoming UEFA Nations League.
